---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Shandapha Changelog"
  description="Migration milestones for the final modernization and continuity architecture."
>
  <section class="section">
    <span class="eyebrow">Migration status</span>
    <h1>Architecture shift in progress</h1>
    <div class="stack-card">
      <div class="step">
        <strong>Registry split</strong>
        <p>Client-safe and server-side registry boundaries now exist as separate workspace packages.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <strong>Generator split</strong>
        <p>Server-side generation core and browser-safe generation preview manifests now have separate homes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <strong>App surface migration</strong>
        <p>Website, docs, wizard, control-plane, sandbox, and demo app targets are being established alongside transitional surfaces.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
